  • Method Details

    • load

      public TiledMap load​(String fileName)
      Loads the TiledMap from the given file. The file is resolved via the FileHandleResolver set in the constructor of this class. By default it will resolve to an internal file. The map will be loaded for a y-up coordinate system.
      Parameters:
      fileName - the filename
      Returns:
      the TiledMap

    • load

      public TiledMap load​(String fileName, TmxMapLoader.Parameters parameter)
      Loads the TiledMap from the given file. The file is resolved via the FileHandleResolver set in the constructor of this class. By default it will resolve to an internal file.
      Parameters:
      fileName - the filename
      parameter - specifies whether to use y-up, generate mip maps etc.
      Returns:
      the TiledMap
